db.execute('INSERT INTO challenges (image_url, description, title, skill_id) VALUES ("https://d3tixod1wp885b.cloudfront.net/67/8f9cfb5541e7be39e9601b0c2cf928/poster.jpg", "Sys Admin\'s often also manage the web servers hosting their organization\'s site. Learn to install a package from source and write a simple server in Node.js. Take a screenshot of your server running locally to complete the challenge.", "Set up a Web Server", 100)')
